Otjiwarongo.title: Otjiwarongo
Otjiwarongo.byline: Otjiwarongo (Otjiherero: "pleasant place" or "place where fat cattle graze") is a city of 28,000 inhabitants (2011) in the Otjozondjupa Region of Namibia.

Otjozondjupa.title: Otjozondjupa
Otjozondjupa.byline: Otjozondjupa is a region in eastern central Namibia.
